WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:02.500
What a bad day.

2
00:00:03.700 --> 00:00:04.500
Mr. Duan,

3
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:05.233
Looks like from now on...

4
00:00:05.266 --> 00:00:06.266
we won’t be seeing each other again.

5
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:08.766
Murderer!

6
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.766
How long are you planning to keep pretending?

7
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.300
Murderer!

8
00:00:14.900 --> 00:00:15.500
Are you alright?

9
00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:16.466
What do you think?

10
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:18.766
Careless work!

11
00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:20.166
Didn’t I tell you already?

12
00:00:20.333 --> 00:00:21.666
Her name is Ye Qi Luo

13
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.366
The daughter of Xiang Jie Group's CEO

14
00:00:25.533 --> 00:00:26.933
No way...

15
00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.100
She’s the one who killed my daughter.

16
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:31.533
Even if she turned to ash, I’d still recognize her.

17
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.666
If the law won’t punish her...

18
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:36.700
...then I will.

19
00:00:38.166 --> 00:00:39.266
Are you done causing trouble?

20
00:00:39.766 --> 00:00:41.466
One more move, and I’ll call the police.

21
00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:45.133
Go ahead, call them.

22
00:00:45.833 --> 00:00:47.100
I’ll ask them myself—

23
00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:49.900
Why would they let a murderer go free?

24
00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:56.366
Murderer?

25
00:00:57.533 --> 00:00:58.333
Criminal?

26
00:00:59.133 --> 00:00:59.800
Is this the gift

27
00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:01.366
your team prepared for me?

28
00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.900
Or is this how your people

29
00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:05.700
treat their guests?

30
00:01:06.766 --> 00:01:07.133
No, that’s not it.

31
00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:07.700
Qi Luo

32
00:01:07.766 --> 00:01:08.666
please let me explain.

33
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.133
Qi Luo

34
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:13.100
Qi Luo

35
00:01:17.166 --> 00:01:17.933
Qi Luo

36
00:01:18.366 --> 00:01:19.133
Listen to me

37
00:01:19.566 --> 00:01:21.066
That woman is insane.

38
00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:22.766
I will definitely report this.

39
00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:23.766
So the higher-ups fire her.

40
00:01:24.633 --> 00:01:25.300
Why so much talking?

41
00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:26.400
Aren’t you just scared...

42
00:01:26.466 --> 00:01:27.766
...I’ll ghost your whole team?

43
00:01:29.900 --> 00:01:31.700
Qi Luo, listen to me

44
00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.166
I sincerely apologize.

45
00:01:35.366 --> 00:01:36.133
Really?

46
00:01:36.766 --> 00:01:38.633
Then I won’t hold back anymore.
